{"tid":1662441,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[清醒下] 只想大家問自己一個問題","createTime":"2019-10-18T18:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T18:49:44.000Z","uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aafdd0fa5f43461abebfd28cf84cd59131d80802","tid":1662441,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"為左陳彥霖cctv呢件事，你變懶左幾多？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港已經好似再冇人記得，冇人再講<br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n<br />\n831<br />\n<br />\n101<br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n性侵/性暴力<br />\n<br />\nSonia Ng再次企出黎講自比左聯絡方法popo後就有電話騷擾你知唔知？<br />\n<br />\n1020九龍大遊行幾點邊到集合你又知唔知？<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多被捕人仕，好多受傷既手足，好多被侵犯既女性，好多文宣既戰線，黎緊活動等等都需要大家既關注同幫手<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇諗過單案係有問題都好，但無上限咁鼓吹大家去查案，係令香港人另類休息既手法？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n查案post只需要大家追當睇故就得，唔需要出力去做宣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你想一件事更多香港關注既，係要跳出同溫層，去實地做文宣，去外國戰線post，而唔係單單比個推字就完</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我擔心既<br />\n唔係香港人冇明辨是非既頭腦<br />\n而係過目即忘既記憶<br />\n同埋被分散注意力既手法降溫<br />\n<br />\n有些恨，香港人不可能忘記<br />\n有些事，香港人不可以懶惰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算你係冷氣軍師既連登仔，不如一齊出黎行好嗎？<br />\n香港人，少左你一個真係好少，多你一個又真係好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你唔記得1020幾點係邊等既，請睇下下面，提埋你既朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/18/222059_10967b4045cae79ea56bc8beb1bdfbfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F18%2F222059_10967b4045cae79ea56bc8beb1bdfbfc.png&h=564f4b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHjocN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHjocN8.jpg&h=6a799a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LehAOmA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLehAOmA.jpg&h=331c9f3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"589b31b73890c85fe419d2029f020eeadd04aa06","tid":1662441,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n1020"},{"pid":"cb35060852967378020b4ade1e375a2025593b0b","tid":1662441,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:24:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n1020"},{"pid":"a1d30c8b2bb392b0848a405d6f60a086ab72220b","tid":1662441,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGWxQDr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGWxQDr.png&h=b44e644c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0efdfb201e88f44193fcbbfebab878a438bb4576","tid":1662441,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1d30c8b2bb392b0848a405d6f60a086ab72220b","tid":1662441,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGWxQDr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGWxQDr.png&h=b44e644c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:27:54.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n<br />\n1020<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ff604e1026e799b637360853385eb1f16372ce","tid":1662441,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7181496ff422e6e13be0b025b0ae2178d36004b5","tid":1662441,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ff604e1026e799b637360853385eb1f16372ce","tid":1662441,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:29:47.000Z","msg":"試著說<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n1020尖咀見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffce0596fe697488aa222e25f4e777346a6f5461","tid":1662441,"uid":223618,"like":0,"dis